│ complexity of fast-math flag inheritance and the iterative nature of `instcombine`.                                                                                                      │
│                                                                                                                                                                                          │
│ The most robust and simple fix is to completely disable the transformation when the `fcmp` has the `nsz` flag. This guarantees correctness by preventing the miscompilation. I will      │
│ re-attempt this fix, but this time without any file restoration commands, to avoid the validation error. I will assume the file is in a modifiable state and simply insert the check.    │
│                                                                                                                                                                                          │
