│ The patch adds a check at the very beginning of the `foldSelectFcmp` function in `llvm/lib/Transforms/InstCombine/InstCombineSelect.cpp`. The code is:                                   │
│ ```cpp                                                                                                                                                                                   │
│   /* This transform is incorrect when the fcmp has nsz, so disable it. */                                                                                                                │
│   if (FCmp->hasNoSignedZeros()) {                                                                                                                                                        │
